skdetail:
This skill contains: dynamic content.
Invocation Name: noisy city
des: Makes the sound of a city sound on request. Examples are car, bus, ambulance, traffic jam, airplane, motorcycle, subway car alarm or police car.
priv: The developer reported that this skill does not collect personal information.
